      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/ecb-decision-to-assess-faster-disinflation-cipollone-tells-orf</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行执委会委员皮耶罗·西波洛内表示，欧洲央行需要在下周的政策会议上评估通货紧缩加快和经济增长放缓的问题。]]></description>
