      <title>亚德尼称美联储今年已完成降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/yardeni-says-the-fed-is-done-cutting-rates-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Yardeni Research 总裁 Ed Yardeni 表示，美联储今年的降息行动已经结束，他预计第三季度的收益将创下历史新高。他正在接受“彭博监测”采访。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/yardeni-says-the-fed-is-done-cutting-rates-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 13:12:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>萨尔瓦多债券因 ESG 债务互换削减成本计划而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/el-salvador-seeks-to-cut-borrowing-costs-with-esg-debt-swap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[萨尔瓦多披露通过债务置换和促进可持续发展来降低借贷成本的计划后，该国债券价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/el-salvador-seeks-to-cut-borrowing-costs-with-esg-debt-swap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 09:58:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储重新考虑利率政策，美国收益率自 8 月以来首次回升至 4%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/key-us-yields-near-4-for-first-time-since-august-on-fed-rethink</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一份出色的就业报告削弱了美联储再次大幅降息的可能性之后，美国主要国债收益率回升至 4%，为 8 月份以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/key-us-yields-near-4-for-first-time-since-august-on-fed-rethink</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 07:41:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马尔代夫重新转向印度以缓解中国债务压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/maldives-seeks-to-repair-ties-with-india-as-debt-crisis-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马尔代夫总统一年前上台，力图将印度排除在该国事务之外，与中国拉近关系。如今，随着债务危机的临近以及中国先前发放的贷款即将到期，他正在新德里寻求修复两国关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/maldives-seeks-to-repair-ties-with-india-as-debt-crisis-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 05:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员减少对美联储降息的押注，股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-after-us-jobs-report-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员削减对美联储降息的押注，导致股市下跌，美国 10 年期国债收益率超过 4%。市场在等待以色列是否会对上周的导弹袭击进行报复，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-after-us-jobs-report-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:37:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>力拓拟以 33 亿美元收购 Arcadium Litium 公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/rio-tinto-confirms-it-s-made-an-approach-to-buy-arcadium-lithium-m1y5cwtw</link>
      <description><![CDATA[双方周一表示，力拓集团 (Rio Tinto Group) 已对 Arcadium Lithium Plc 发出收购要约，确认了这一最新收购提议。目前，该行业正将注意力重新转向增长，各大矿业公司都在竞相增加对能源过渡金属的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/rio-tinto-confirms-it-s-made-an-approach-to-buy-arcadium-lithium-m1y5cwtw</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:20:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
